Model:Vitals.Model:CVP: last CVP from #now - 4 h to #now carry 8 hours
Model:Vitals.Model:CVP Delta: (mean CVP from #now - 4 h to #now) - (mean CVP from #now - 8 h to #now - 4 h)

Model:Vitals.Model:GCS:
(last GCSTotal from #now - 4 h to #now carry 8 hours) impute (
    (last GCSEye from #now - 4 h to #now impute mean) + 
    (last GCSMotor from #now - 4 h to #now impute mean) +
    (last GCSVerbal from #now - 4 h to #now impute mean)
    carry 8 hours
)
Model:Vitals.Model:GCS Delta:
((last GCSTotal from #now - 4 h to #now) impute (
    (last GCSEye from #now - 4 h to #now impute mean) + 
    (last GCSMotor from #now - 4 h to #now impute mean) +
    (last GCSVerbal from #now - 4 h to #now impute mean)
)) - ((last GCSTotal from #now - 8 h to #now - 4 h) impute (
    (last GCSEye from #now - 8 h to #now - 4 h impute mean) + 
    (last GCSMotor from #now - 8 h to #now - 4 h impute mean) +
    (last GCSVerbal from #now - 8 h to #now - 4 h impute mean)
))
Model:Vitals.Model:GCS Present: exists union(GCSEye, GCSMotor, GCSVerbal) from #now - 4 h to #now or exists GCSTotal from #now - 4 h to #now
